Package: TestContR
Type: Package
Title: Select Test and Control groups
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alfredo G Marquez
Maintainer: Alfredo G Marquez <alfredo.g.marquez@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), random (>= 0.2.6), tidyverse (>= 1.2.1), reshape2 (>= 1.4.3)
Description: Select a random list of test group and provides the best matching group for a control based on a dataframe of metrics for the subjects.  
    Currently, only numeric values are excepted since Euclidian distance is used for the pairing.  Categorical variables coming later.
License: MIT
Copyright: all rights reservedS
LazyData: true
BuildVignettes: FALSE
